import React from 'react'; import { useLocation, useNavigate } from 'react-router-dom'; import './css/ThankYou.css'; const ThankYou = () => { const location = useLocation(); const navigate = useNavigate(); const { orderId, cartGrandTotal, cartItems, checkoutDetails, discountApplied, pointsRedeemed, amountSavedAgainstMRP, groupedItems, paymentMethod, amountReturned } = location.state || { orderId: 'N/A', cartGrandTotal: 0, cartItems: [], checkoutDetails: {}, discountApplied: 0, pointsRedeemed: 0, amountSavedAgainstMRP: 0, groupedItems: [], paymentMethod: 'N/A', amountReturned: 0 }; const handleNewOrder = () => { navigate('/poscart'); }; // Calculate total items and total quantity const totalItems = cartItems.length; const totalQuantity = cartItems.reduce((sum, item) => sum + item.quantity, 0); // For demonstration, let's assume current date for order date const orderDate = new Date().toLocaleDateString(); return (

TAX INVOICE

Order no: {orderId}

Order Date: {orderDate}

Store: {checkoutDetails.store || 'N/A'}

Cashier: {checkoutDetails.cashier || 'N/A'}

Product List

{cartItems.map((item, index) => ( ))}
SKU Product Name Qty N/Rate Value
{item.sku_id || 'N/A'} {item.productName} {item.quantity} {item.market_rate ? item.market_rate.toFixed(2) : 'N/A'} {(item.quantity * item.price).toFixed(2)}

Items: {totalItems}

Qty: {totalQuantity}

SubTotal: ₹ {cartGrandTotal.toFixed(2)}

{groupedItems.length > 0 && (

GST Breakup Details

{groupedItems.map((group, index) => ( ))}
GST IND Taxable Amount CGST SGST Total Amount
{index + 1} {group.taxableAmount.toFixed(2)} {group.cgst.toFixed(2)} {group.sgst.toFixed(2)} {group.totalAmount.toFixed(2)}
)}

Discount Applied: ₹ {discountApplied.toFixed(2)}

Points Redeemed: ₹ {pointsRedeemed.toFixed(2)}

←Amount Recd. From customer→

Payment Mode: {paymentMethod}

Final Total: ₹ {cartGrandTotal.toFixed(2)}

{amountReturned > 0 && (

Change Due: ₹ {amountReturned.toFixed(2)}

)}
{amountSavedAgainstMRP > 0 && (

** Saved Rs. {amountSavedAgainstMRP.toFixed(2)} on MRP **

)}

Thank You for Your Order!

); }; export default ThankYou;
